Creating a API Gateway

1.Go to API Gateway >> create API >> HTTP API >>>build  
  >>Give it a name[ImageUploaderApi]
2.Select the ip address type
  >>ipv4
  >>dualstack [Both ipv4 and ipv6]

3.Integration [specify the backend service that your API will communicate with ,These are called integrations .]
   >>select the lambda function
     >>region and the version

4.configure the route
Method 
*Post
Resource Path
*/uploads
integration target
*amith-lambda

**you can add addtionall route

5.Define stage -optional[no idea right known]

Then click create



  

